author: Jake Maxwell Watts
title: Trans-Pacific Trade Deal to Prod South East Asia
text:
SINGAPORE—A major trade accord signed Monday is likely to bring its signatories in Southeast Asia politically and economically closer to the U.S. while pressuring them to loosen long-standing regulations on business and labor.
